      "content": "wait, what? i think there was a glitch in your last response. i'm talking about actual inventory loss in a warehouse, not fantasy stuff. can you please ignore the goblin thing and just give me the actual professional reasons for these discrepancies? like, what are the standard logistical causes for these kinds of weekly variances?",
